data.description: Great location! Nestled in a private street, this lock and leave townhouse features an open floor plan, tray ceilings, crown molding, stained concrete floors, granite countertops, neutral colors throughout, convenient half bath on the main floor, large backyard with privacy fence and plenty of storage. The oversized master suite that can be converted into the original third bedroom. Near the Medical Center, Loop 410, USAA and UTSA.
